title: Match history not showing up?
body:
so in the first screenshot shows my match history, yet 3 games don't show up? in the second screenshot is lolking and what it should look like...
how can i fix this?

Hey guys

We were troubleshooting a couple of minor issues with match history around the time of your post.  Have the missing matches shown up for you now?

Mindstar
yeah the history has popped up now! cheers Mindstar.
